See our disclaimer |UnderTech UnderCover Womens Concealed Carry Short Shorts The UnderTech UnderCover "SHORT SHORTS" feature a 2" inseam and are now available due to popular demand by our Federal Law Enforcement customers. The UnderTech UnderCover "SHORT SHORTS" feature the same comfortable, form fitting, compression fabric in our original shorts, yet are 2" inches shorter in the leg to allow you to wear shorter clothing. They will even stay concealed under workout shorts. The "SHORT SHORTS" feature two concealment pockets, one on each side to accommodate both right and left hand shooters. They are extremely comfortable and will enable you to carry and conceal a handgun without having to wear an unsightly "Gun Belt" or protruding holster. This is absolutely the most comfortable concealment option ever.....you will forget you are carrying and concealing a handgun! This is the perfect way for women to carry and conceal a handgun when theyre wearing a skirt or slacks without a belt. Modeled off our extremely popular Compression T-Shirt, this Compression Concealment Shorts Holster is custom built on a pair of name brand compression shorts that are made specifically for a womans body. Its extremely comfortable, secure and yet so concealed. It can be worn with just about everything you own, gym shorts, sweat pants, slacks, skirts, and suits. Because it works without a belt, it finally gives women a truly remarkable concealment option. Each pair of shorts features two identical holsters, one on each side, so if youre right handed you can carry a handgun on your right side and also carry spare magazines, documents, handcuffs on your left side. And, vise versa for left handed individuals. Truly one of the most comfortable holsters youll ever wear. Extremely popular with female federal agents, undercover officers, and parole officers. Available in Black, White and Nude. Allows you to carry and conceal any self-defense handgun. Made in USA, MicroPoly/Lycra blend, machine washable. How To Care For Your UTUC Garments: Machine wash in cold water. Air or tumble dry on low. Air drying is preferred as it will extend the life of your garment. Do not use fabric softener.
